		<description><![CDATA[Are you neglecting your health and only focusing on your kids?]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<small>(Click title to listen)</small><br /><p>HALF-HOUR PODCAST SUMMARY:</p>
<p>When raising teenagers, we tend to focus on the kids and their needs.  But positive family relationships won’t happen if mom and dad aren’t taking care of themselves!  Today on <em>Parenting Today’s Teens</em>, Mark Gregston shares practical steps for becoming healthy parents with healthy kids.</p>
<p>Special Guest: Dr. Robert Epstein</p>
