		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.heartlightministries.org/blogs/pttradio/?p=6280</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Are you relying on God's strength with your parenting?]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<small>(Click title to listen)</small><br /><p>PODCAST SCRIPT:</p>
<p>When it seems like nothing’s goin’ right at home… when your teen is spinning out of control… ever feel like throwing up your hands and walking away?</p>
<p>Yeah, raising healthy kids is tough business.  And I meet a lot of parents who are confused, tired and frustrated.  They long for easier days.</p>
<p>Well, there’s no one who can wave a magic wand over your household and make it all better… but there <em>is</em> One who can change you from the inside out.  So when you feel like giving up… it’s the perfect time to depend on God.</p>
<p>So instead of getting hassled over the trials at home … turn to the only One who can help you.  See this as a grand adventure for God to do His greatest work … in <em>you</em>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
