		<link>http://www.heartlightministries.org/blogs/pttradio/2012/03/15/explore-activities-3152012-2/</link>
		<comments>http://www.heartlightministries.org/blogs/pttradio/2012/03/15/explore-activities-3152012-2/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Thu, 15 Mar 2012 10:00:01 +0000</pubDate>
