		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.heartlightministries.org/blogs/pttradio/?p=6009</guid>
		<description><![CDATA[Time invested in your teen can be very rewarding.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<small>(Click title to listen)</small><br /><p>PODCAST SCRIPT:</p>
<p>What are your hobbies?  What do you spend your Saturday afternoons doing?  Now… one more question:  Are you putting the same effort into connecting with your teen, that you’re pouring into your favorite pastime?</p>
<p>We all need time to rest, relax and do the things we like best.  But here’s an idea.  Why not do it with your teen, as well?  Take time to find out what your son or daughter likes… and do it with them.  Or… if you can’t find some common ground, explore a new activity together!</p>
<p>The time you invest in your teen will be abundantly rewarding.  And… who knows?  You just might find a new hobby!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
